title: Sample Book (France), 1935–38
provenance: Imported from France by Barrie and Desmond, Inc. of New York, NY.
description: 43 examples of wallpaper, some of which have color alternates. 8 have border and chair rail schemes attached. Included are designs in the style of the late 18th century and French Empire period. Several "plaid" and marbleized patterns, also.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (France), 1935–38; Distributed by Barrie and Desmond, Inc. ; block-printed; 1953-147-1-1/76
